    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle St</name>
                    <date when="1887-02-04">Feb: 4 '87</date>
                    <name type="place">—Camden New Jersey U S America<ptr target="bms.00002_n1"/></name>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>I find that the whole book "Specimen Days &amp; Collect"—as I sent it to
                you—338 pages (without the Appendix)—makes about as much as y'r "History
                of King Arthur" Volume<ptr target="bms.00002_n2"/>—If you &amp; the publisher
                prefer to pub. it all in <hi rend="italic">one volume</hi>, you can do so.<ptr target="bms.00002_n3"/></p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
